{"tid":2433321,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美智庫：近9成美國人視中國為「對手」 多數支持對中強硬","createTime":"2021-03-05T00:46:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T15:50:48.000Z","uid":141151,"like":57,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"074d9b0b488916b4a3fc660d60b71f82e53bd32f","tid":2433321,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T00:46:11.000Z","msg":"美智庫：近9成美國人視中國為「對手」 多數支持對中強硬<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3456820\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3456820&d=eRHmMhW6fCYgFX7Mu85bUgRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=b2b924f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3456820&h=0910e5ed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3456820</a><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國智庫「皮尤」當地時間4日發布一份美中關係調查，內容為詢問美國人對中國各項議題的看法。<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">結果顯示，近9成受訪者視中國為競爭對手而非夥伴；多數認為美國應在人權、經濟等問題上對中國表達強硬態度。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n報告寫道，89％的美國公民視中國為競爭對手而非夥伴；多數人支持美國應對中國採取更強勢作法，包含70％的人認為即便損害經貿關係，也要提升中國人權；55％支持限制中國留學生赴美就學；53％同意在經濟議題上對中國強硬。此外，48％的人認為限制中國及其影響力是美國外交政策首要任務，較2018年的32％上升16％。<br />\n<br />\n以0至100分來評價對中國的好感度，67％受訪者呈現的趨勢為冷感（不到50分），較2018年的46％要高上許多，當中非常不佳（不到25分）的比例更從23％倍增為47％。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">若詢問受訪者想到中國的第一件事為何？20％的回答為「人權」、19％「經濟」、17％「政治體系」，其中另有9％及3％確切說出「缺乏自由」及「新疆種族滅絕」，顯示中國人權是美國民眾最關切的議題。<br />\n<br />\n</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"915144fbd5d87f8c20851f1ff506eb060cee2c95","tid":2433321,"uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T00:46:42.000Z","msg":"開始醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e4d1829613187dc8cc8abe50baa7bb53f8860e8","tid":2433321,"uid":72085,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T00:47:33.000Z","msg":"當權既人同埋華爾街太多利益係中國，加上大陸唔理美國人，直接收買對方高層"},{"pid":"85755d44c1584dd8aee6956fc17f111529d22df4","tid":2433321,"uid":127575,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T00:47:33.000Z","msg":"美國左膠：<br />\n請唔好歧視中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中國人權最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港新疆抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a76fbc1c61d6aa602c625d2b900605bb46b3a766","tid":2433321,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T00:48:32.000Z","msg":"China Joe：唔可以歧視中國，要同中國合作<br />\n <img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/-EZ8T06iNl4/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F-EZ8T06iNl4%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=3323aaed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/9oiieqfZ81M/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F9oiieqfZ81M%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=ea7e8534&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0a8bf688ce88780d938478a4bc4f74ebbd105e83","tid":2433321,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T00:49:07.000Z","msg":"10%=迪士尼，華爾街，apple"},{"pid":"3de7f38ae852d34f6ec442a0095df844cf3cf1a9","tid":2433321,"uid":51583,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T00:49:44.000Z","msg":"侵功不可沒<br />\n佢既影響一直都在"},{"pid":"9a2f4700cbe4c6fa959b91432796b3f9fa3601bd","tid":2433321,"uid":51583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a8bf688ce88780d938478a4bc4f74ebbd105e83","tid":2433321,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T00:49:07.000Z","msg":"10%=迪士尼，華爾街，apple"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T00:50:30.000Z","msg":"首先要美國人先抵制親中公司"},{"pid":"e3b6d2d47ceba1fcf7789fd4138d0ce41113d3e6","tid":2433321,"uid":34602,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3de7f38ae852d34f6ec442a0095df844cf3c